MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 274

RESERVING A PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN WITHIN THE MUNICIPALITIES OF DAUIS AND PANGLAO, ISLAND OF PANGLAO, PROVINCE OF BOHOL FOR TOURISM ESTATE DEVELOPMENT PURPOSES AND SHALL BE KNOWN AS PANGLAO ISLAND TOURISM ESTATE (PITE)

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and pursuant to the powers vested upon me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby reserve certain parcels of land of the public domain within the Municipalities of Dauis and Panglao, Island of Panglao, Province of Bohol and reserving the same for Tourism Estate Development Purposes, and shall be known as Panglao Island Tourism Estate (PITE) under the administration and control of the Department of Tourism, subject to actual ground survey and valid private rights, if any there be, which parcel of land more particularly described as follows:

“A parcel of land (SK-07-000022, consisting of ten (10) plans), situated in Barangays of Tawala, Liba-ong and Bolod, all of Municipality of Panglao; and in Barangays of Tinago, San Isidro (formerly Canlongon), Dao and Biking, all of Municipality of Dauis, Island of Panglao, Province of Bohol. Bounded on the SW., along lines 1-2-3-4-5 by Road Center, on the NW., & SW., along lines 5-6-7 by lots 4479, 4478, 5096-B, 4470, 4460, 4462, 4461, 4450, 4451, 4445, 4432, 4431, & Lot 4411, on point 6 by PITE No. 2. on the SW., along line 7-8 by Lots 4411, 4399, 4386, 4385, 4381, 4382, 4372, 4368, 4359, 4358, 4357, 4337, 4336, 4323, 4322, 4320, & Lot 4312; on point 8 by ROAD CENTER: along line 8-9 by Lots 4312, 4311, 4313, 4314, 4304, 4301, 4291, 4283, 5137, 5136, 5133, 5132, & Lot 5118 all of Brgy. Tawala, Panglao, Bohol, on point 9 by PITE No. 3, on point 10 by Road Center (National Highway) on the NW., along line 10-11 by Brgy. of Bolod, Panglao, Bohol, on the NE., & SE., along lines 11 to 18 by Road Center (Barangay Road), on the NE,. along lines 18-19-20 by Brgy. of Bolod, Panglao, Bohol, on point 19 by PITE No. 6, on the NW., along lines 20 to 26 by Lots 5388, 5397, 5394, 5403, 5404, 6271, 6270, & Lot 6277, all of Brgys. of Bolod and Liba-ong, Panglao, Bohol, on point 26 by PITE No. 18, on the SW., along line 26-27 by School Site, and Brgy. of Liba-ong, Panglao, Bohol, with Brgy. Road, on point 27, by PITE No. 27, on the NW., & SW., along lines 27 to 32 by Lots 6359, 6360, 6361, 6375 and Lot 6339, all of Brgy. Liba-ong, Panglao, Bohol, on the NE., & NW., along lines 32-33-34 by Lots 3382, 3375, 3500, 3377, 3340, 3337, and Lot 3338, all of Brgy. Dao, Dauis, Bohol, Gss-07-02-000031; on the NE., along line 34-35 by Existing Road; on the NE., & NW., along lines 35-36-37 by Brgy. of Dao, Dauis, Bohol, on the NE., along lines 38 to 45 by Road Center, on point 45 by PITE No. 21, on the NW., along line 45-46 by Lots 2963, 2962, 2958, 2900, 2998, 2517, 2905, 2516, 2523, 2524, 2560,